{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781222497370,"sessionID":"ses_146f588daffevjMyKj6QyGVWyX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_vp2qblcc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"README.md","content":"```markdown\n# Temperature Conversion CLI Tool\n\n## Installation\n```bash\npip install .\n```\n\n## Usage\nConvert temperatures using the following commands:\n\n### Celsius to Fahrenheit\n```bash\nconvert --from celsius --to fahrenheit <value>\n```\nExample:\n```bash\nconvert --from celsius --to fahrenheit 0\n```\n\n### Fahrenheit to Celsius\n```bash\nconvert --from fahrenheit --to celsius <value>\n```\nExample:\n```bash\nconvert --from fahrenheit --to celsius 212\n```\n\n### Celsius to Kelvin\n```bash\nconvert --from celsius --to kelvin <value>\n```\nExample:\n```bash\nconvert --from celsius --to kelvin 273.15\n```\n\n## Conversion Options\n- `--from`: Specify the input unit (celsius, fahrenheit)\n- `--to`: Specify the output unit (fahrenheit, celsius, kelvin)\n- `<value>`: The numerical value to convert\n\nThe CLI tool uses the following functions:\n- `celsius_to_fahrenheit()`: Converts Celsius to Fahrenheit\n- `fahrenheit_to_celsius()`: Converts Fahrenheit to Celsius\n- `celsius_to_kelvin()`: Converts Celsius to Kelvin\n```"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/nathangreen/Development/eddi-lab/llm-orc/scratch/spike-pi-form-adequacy-gate/B_live/ws_2/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"scratch/spike-pi-form-adequacy-gate/B_live/ws_2/README.md","time":{"start":1781222497360,"end":1781222497368}},"id":"prt_eb9225c41001afKnXuwCGAAiMH","sessionID":"ses_146f588daffevjMyKj6QyGVWyX","messageID":"msg_eb920387e0012Qloy84oYbcZnu"}}
